v9

## Changes

* Removes support for the unstable Nix versions, since they have been superseded by the stable 2.4 release.

* Adds support for Nix 2.0.4 (released in 2018).

* Added convenience flake outputs to allow users to build or run any version of Nix locally:
  https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/tree/v9#using-specific-nix-versions-locally
